description:
Susan Boyle's Christmas Carol Do You Hear What I Hear.


Wintersbutterfly.com

(WordPress Blog)

Just a track in GarageBand


I must have started singing back in Church. I remember sitting once with my Choir Minister. I have Dissociative Amnesia. I can remember sometimes just a bit out of a situation. I can usually see a small excerpt of what happened in great detail. But usually just a small scene. When I was 14 my best friend died. I know that I intentional set my memories aside. I thought I had to protect him, even in Heaven...that I had to protect even God.
